      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>tomato[es]</strong> finely</p><p>Chop your <strong>basil</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped tomato </strong>to a bowl with your <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong>, <strong>chopped basil </strong>and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong> and mix it all together – this is your <strong>balsamic tomato & basil salad</strong></p>",
